::Battera::

She closed her link.  She heard the other voice respond to the 
message.  She didn't need to overhear a conversation that wasn't ment 
for her.  She still stood on the ramp of the ship looking out over 
thee landscape.  She was hoping the war wouldn't destroy all the 
beauty that the land had to offer.
